social_posts.post_text: Looking forward to seeing you all!!!✂️

Some of the best skincare I’ve tried!
The roller and Moisturizing Renewal Night Cream are next level! Cannot wait to try the entire line. 
Thank you  @reviveskincare & @ciankconnor
“It’s gotta be rock ‘n’ roll music if you wanna dance with me” - Chuck Berry 💃🏻😎🕺🏽 @lisarinna @sallyhershberger24k✂️
RIP Barbara🕊️🙏🏻🤍 This was the day that you came into my salon for a shag haircut:) being with you was always a highlight of my day! you were a true pioneer!!! legend! may you rest in peace🕊️🤍🙏🏻🤍
Absolutely devastated by the passing of my dear friend, Tatjana Patitz💔Rip peace🤍🙏🏻🕊️my thoughts go out to her family. Tatjana you will be missed immensely.💔💔💔💔💔💔

Saddened by the passing of Lisa Marie Presley, she was always a pleasure to work with, she was a cool girl, so real and authentic and kind…I can’t believe we just saw her at the Golden Globes two nights ago… and now she’s gone 💔way too young to leave. Sending tons of love to her family.🤍🕊️🙏🏻
I spoke to @voguebeauty on the hottest hair trends from this year’s #NYFW - head over there now to see my favorite looks, the best hair color trends and more!
Can’t wait! And happy to be a part of this!
Thanks @accesshollywood @people @andilavs for including @sallyhershberger24K in your summer hair essentials segment

Happy Birthday David Bowie! I shot these images for David’s album cover with Tin Machine. This was one of the highlights of my life!!! I recently had decided in the height of my hairdressing career to be a photographer, in my late 20s and you/ David took a chance on me to shoot your album cover, what a highlight in my life! and I remember you took me into the recording studio so I could hear your album and you went through the different songs, describing what they were really saying…obviously it was way over my head, you are such a genius, and by far the coolest…these memories will forever live in my heart❤️#grateful
